<TEXT>
millions of people around the globe bade farewell to a 
tumultuous 1990 and embraced the new year with fireworks and gala 
celebrations while their leaders appealed for a peaceful solution 
to the persian gulf crisis 
paris celebrated the 12th stroke of midnight noisily with 
