dostoevski after all came very close to a firing squad and 
spent a lot of time locked up and during that time he wrote in 
letters to friends that he had come to feel the need for faith like 
parched earth does and had found it because as he wrote truth 
shines in misfortune 
rushdie insisted he would not repudiate the satanic verses 
