withdraw it from circulation 
it seems to me whats very important is that the book should 
remain in print so that in time it can be appreciated as something 
other than the book it has been made out to be i dont repudiate 
the book what ive said is and what ive been explaining over and 
over again for two years is that its been much misunderstood and 
that i am trying now by canceling the paperback to create what i 
call a pause for understanding 
