alternative forum to correct the behavior of kids 
the program launched last month after more than a year of 
planning is modeled after ones in odessa texas and tarrytown 
ny but denver is the first major city to implement the program 
the sixmember juries impose real sentences in a real courtroom 
presided over by a retired juvenile court judge the lawyers and 
