theirs was an egalitarian marriage though he always outearned 
her bank accounts were separate his assistant billed her monthly 
for her share of the food utilities and schnauzergrooming bills 
she testified 
in 1979 snyder created an imprint a semiautonomous shop 
within a larger publishing house called linden press for evans to 
