the soldier stood at the memorial marked with the 
names of vietnams valleys of death khe sanh and con thien hue 
and quang tri an loc and xuan loc 
then nguyen ngoc hung lighted a dozen incense sticks and 
silently faced his fallen american foes memorialized in the stone 
