wic directors said baby formula prices have seemed to go up in 
lock step over the last 10 years 
betsy clarke director of the wic program in oregon said prices 
have tripled during the past 15 years with different companies 
raising prices by the same amounts within days of each other 
current retail prices range from 180 to 230 for a 13ounce 
can of concentrated formula 
