maturities rose 316 point to 932 point intermediate maturities 
rose rsqb point to 716 point and longterm issues were up 1732 point 
to 1116 point telerate inc reported 
the movement of a point is equivalent to a change of 10 in the 
price of a bond with a 1000 face value 
